               </foaf:name><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by/></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by> He was one of the Nine Saints, a group of foreign monks who arrived in Ethiopia
                     in the 5th and 6th century. 
                     After he arrived with the other saints, he is believed to have settled in the southeast of 
                     ʿAdwā.
